Package org.timepedia.chronoscope.client

Interface Summary
ChronoscopeMenu Implement this and ChronoscopeMenuFactory to create alternative popup menus for Chronoscope.
ChronoscopeMenuFactory Implement this to swap out the types of popup menus created by Chronoscope
Overlay Interface implemented by Markers and other clases which overlay the plot
XYDataset An interface modeling a multiresolution dataset of two coordinates

A multiresolution dataset is a dataset consisting of multiple levels, with level 0 being the bottom most level containing the original datasets.
XYDataSourceFactory  
XYPlot An interface to be implemented by classes implementing XY plots of XY Datasets.
XYPlotListener Implement this interface to track state changes in a Plot
